{"tid":542863,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普：WOW！只得怪自己","createTime":"2018-01-28T02:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T03:57:40.000Z","uid":333,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ad9380c78a7c9022cfb868122ebdf19f5ee994","tid":542863,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=a0EL2TqwfpJ7CvUbxbS21hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=bb99ad37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】一個WOW，道出利物浦領隊高普對球隊的防守表現有多意外，他認為紅軍出局只能怪自己。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦剛在足總盃以2:3被西布朗踢出局，領隊高普賽後說：「我們做錯了甚麼是顯而易見，第2個失球，實在是整個團隊的差勁防守，這不是該有的防守。」其實當紅軍落後1:2時獲得12碼，只是法明奴射高波中楣彈出，之後更失守致落後1:3，乃輸波的轉捩點。<br />\n<br />\n為此，高普自是滿腹牢騷：「我們沒有把握12碼的機會，然後對方的第3個入球肯定是越位，我們可以做甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n「我們在下半場該展示個性，努力追趕，或許第2個入球來得太遲。當你作出這樣的開始，就難以踢出最好的足球。」紅軍在聯賽大落後，保前4似乎較實際，而國內兩個盃賽都已出局，如今歐聯成為本季僅有的冠軍希望。"},{"pid":"8fad41746bb9ffe41bb2d6915572ec00ef074ba8","tid":542863,"uid":10176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"拎75m搶Laporte過黎<br />\n再拎75m買oblak<br />\n英超在望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ab7bd50e33deb99a6a154e32e73b4d991d8380","tid":542863,"uid":106165,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"睇埋var都話offside<br />\n猁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b60031e52bcc2a22d55ffa2824de41c45bf5f2","tid":542863,"uid":73067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"Offside<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0409288bc6762278b8478c2ba1a97f65b0a2461a",